title: Tertangkap Kamera! Gerak-gerik Pelaku Sebelum Tembak Shinzo Abe dari Belakang
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota. https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Sebuah video amatir beredar luas di media social yang memperlihatkan gerak-gerik Tetsuya Yamagami seorang pelaku penembakan mantan Perdana Menteri Shinzo Abe.||||Dalam video itu, pelaku yang memakai baju abu-abu serta masker berwarna putih berada di belakang Shinzo Abe.||||Dia berdiri sambil memerhatikan situasi di sekitar sebelum melakukan aksinya. ||||Pelaku yang bernama Tetsuya Yamagami ini terlihat selalu melirik ke arah kanan dan kiri untuk memastikan situasi aman. ||||Sebelumnya, mantan Perdana Menteri Shinzo Abe tertembak 2 kali saat sedang pidato.||||Baca Juga Berduka, SBY Kenang Mendiang Mantan PM Jepang Shinzo Abe: Pemimpin Hebat! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307376/berduka-sby-kenang-mendiang-mantan-pm-jepang-shinzo-abe-pemimpin-hebat||||Dia pun dinyatakan meninggal akibat insiden tersebut.||Pelaku yang bernama Tetsuya Yamagami pun langsung dibekuk aparat keamanan.||||Video Editor: Lintang || ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307391/tertangkap-kamera-gerak-gerik-pelaku-sebelum-tembak-shinzo-abe-dari-belakang

title: 16 killed, 40 Missing After Cloudburst Trigger Flash Flood In Amarnath Camp | Amarnath Clouburst
description: 16 people were killed and 40 were missing after a flash flood triggered by a cloudburst hit a camp near the Amarnath cave shrine in J&Kâ€™s Ganderbal district on July 8. The cloudburst occurred around 6 pm, and the flash flood washed away a part of the camp with officials estimating that at least 25 tents were hit. title: 'Alaska is ours' billboards in Russia after Putin aide vows to reclaim territory I Watch Reactions
description: A day after key Putin aide Vyacheslav Volodin threatens to take back Alaska from the US in retaliation for its sanctions against Moscow, several billboards appeared in the Russian city of Krasnoyarsk reading 'Alaska is ours'. However, these posters are not put up by the Russian govt. As per a report in Newsweek, these billboards were placed by a local company named 'Alaska'. Remember, on 30th March 1867, Russia sold Alaska to the US for $7.2 million. Watch this video to know more.|#alaska #biden #putin #billboards #vyacheslavvolodin #alaskaisours #moscow #krasnoyarsk

title: Pakistan 'sinking': Govt debt rises by over 15%; Gas tariff surges by a staggering 235%
description: Crisis-hit Pak's total debt increased by 15.3% in the first 11 months of FY22. 44.638 trillion Pakistani Rupees debt in May v/s 38.704 trillion PKR in June 2021. Pak Central Bank's foreign exchange reserves fell by $493MN (week ending June 30). Pakistan's overall foreign exchange holdings also fell to $15.742 billion. Pak caught in a vicious cycle - burgeoning debt hindering recovery & development. title: NEW STADIUM DRONE UPDATE | Latest aerial footage as fresh steelwork fitted at Bramley-Moore Dock
description: New steelwork has emerged at the south end of Evertonâ€™s new stadium at Bramley-Moore Dock.|The shape of the stadium bowl on the waterfront development is growing ever clearer, as can be seen from this weekâ€™s revealing drone shots of the site.|The fresh latticework of steelwork rising adjacent to the south west core, along with a similar build expected to start soon in the south east corner, will next month connect to a third, larger steel structure that is currently spreading outwards from the centre of the one-tier south stand. This â€˜home endâ€™ will eventually house approximately 13,000 Evertonians.|Raking beams that angle down towards the â€˜pitchâ€™ are the steel on which precast concrete terracing units will be lowered in the coming months.|The highest current point of the central block of steelwork is the external frame of the glazed South Stand Bar, which will look back towards the city centre.|New tiers of steelwork are also now visible in the north west corner of the stadium, where concrete lattice slabs are already laid on two levels.|The two separate sections of steelwork in the north stand are due to conjoin in early August.|Meanwhile, work on the west stand has seen more concrete foundation slabs and precast walls installed in the embryonic structure.|Within two months, it is anticipated that the ground floor level of the build will be visible along the majority of the west stand.|Subscribe to Everton Football Club's official YouTube Channel: http://bit.ly/2wtCEbB|Follow us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/everton|Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/everton|Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/everton|Welcome to the Official Everton Football Club YouTube channel. title: A look at 7 world leaders shockingly assassinated | Israel, U.S & India on the list
description: The assassination of former Japanese prime minister Shinzo Abe during a campaign speech has again brought into focus the killings of several heads of state and top leaders globally including two Indian prime ministers, Indira Gandhi and Rajiv Gandhi. In 1984, Indira Gandhi was assassinated by two of her security guards. Years later, her son and former prime minister Rajiv Gandhi too was assassinated in 1991. Among other heads of state around the world who have been assassinated, including leaders from Pakistan, Nepal, Sri Lanka and the US. title: Kenapa Mantan PM Jepang Shinzo Abe Ditembak hingga Meninggal? Ini Kata Pengamat
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota. https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Pengamat Hubungan Internasional Hikmahanto Juwana menilai penembakan ini diduga karena mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang Shinzo Abe ingin amandemen konstitusi Jepang menjadi negara remiliterisasi.||||"Kemungkinan berkaitan dengan vokalnya mantan Perdana Menteri Shinzo Abe terkait keinginan beliau melakukan amandemen dalam mengubah pasal 9 konstitusi Jepang yang berisi yaitu mengatur tentang Jepang tidak boleh memiliki alat perang dan membuat negara Jepang sebagai negara Asia Pasifis dan banyak masyarakat menyetujuinya," kata Hikmahanto.||||Hal ini didasarkan oleh perkembangan jaman maka Shinzo Abe ingin Jepang seperti negara lainnya, namun hal ini ditolak oleh beberapa negara yang pernah dijajah oleh Jepang.||||"Tapi kita perlu melihat juga apakah ini warga negara Jepang atau bukan. Karena dari negara lain tidak ingin melakukan remiliterisasi. Terutama Negara-negara yg pernah dijajah oleh Jepang." Ujarnya.||||Baca Juga Jepang Berkabung, Jasad Shinzo Abe Dibawa Pulang ke Tokyo di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307341/jepang-berkabung-jasad-shinzo-abe-dibawa-pulang-ke-tokyo||||Sebelumnya, Shinzo Abe ditembak dua kali pada saat pidato di kampanye pemilihan majelis tinggi.||||Saat itu terdengar suara tembakan cukup keras ke arah mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang yang 2 tahun lalu mengundurkan diri.||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani || ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307366/kenapa-mantan-pm-jepang-shinzo-abe-ditembak-hingga-meninggal-ini-kata-pengamat

title: Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah Tak ada Aktivitas, Para Santri telah Dijemput Keluarga
description: JOMBANG, KOMPAS.TV - Suasana di sekitar Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah Jombang tampak lengang setelah izin operasional dicabut Kementerian Agama. Polisi yang sempat berjaga di sekitar pesantren juga telah ditarik ke satuannya masing-masing.||||Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah di Ploso Kabupaten Jombang Jawa Timur tampak lengang usai upaya penjemputan paksa yang dilakukan polisi Kamis 7 Juli 2022.||||Baca Juga Kemenang Cabut Izin Ponpes Shiddiqiyyah, PWNU Jatim : Jangan Ada Kesan Pesantren Ajarkan Pelecehan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307256/kemenang-cabut-izin-ponpes-shiddiqiyyah-pwnu-jatim-jangan-ada-kesan-pesantren-ajarkan-pelecehan||||Tidak tampak kegiatan yang mencolok di pesantren setelah izin operasional pesantren dicabut Kementerian Agama.||||Pintu masuk samping pesantren yang sebelumnya dijaga ketat aparat kepolisian juga telah dibuka sehingga warga mulai bisa beraktivitas kembali.||||Pintu masuk samping pesantren ini merupakan gang pemukiman warga||||untuk mengetahui kondisi terkini di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, kita terhubung dengan Jurnalis KompasTV Muhammad Syafiuddin di Jombang Jawa Timur. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307385/pesantren-shiddiqiyyah-tak-ada-aktivitas-para-santri-telah-dijemput-keluarga

title: Jalan Panjang Santriwati Menuntut Keadilan
description: Kasus pencabulan santri dengan tersangka MSAT yang dikenal sebagai Mas Bechi ini sudah dilaporkan ke polisi pada 2018. Para korban yang merupakan santri perempuan ini, menempuh jalan panjang untuk mendapatkan keadilan, agar Mas Bechi yang telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka, diproses hukum. Kita simak laporan khas redaksi.

title: Rishi Sunak formally announces UK PM bid with #Ready4Rishi campaign I Key Details
description: British Indian former Finance Minister Rishi Sunak has formally launched his leadership bid to become the next Prime Minister of Britain. Sunak launched the #Ready4Rishi campaign bid on Twitter. Sunak is seen as a credible contender and a frontrunner in some conservative party quarters. The 42-year-old MP is the son-in-law of Infosys co-founder Narayana Murthy. Watch this video to know more.|#rishisunak #uk #britain #primeminister #10downingstreet #fomerfinanceminister #conservativeparty #infosys

title: Izin Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah Dicabut, Bagaimana Nasib Santri? | AKIP tvOne
description: Jakarta, https://www.tvOnenews.com - Izin Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah Dicabut, Bagaimana Nasib Santri? | AKIP tvOne|Kementerian Agama resmi mencabut izin operasional Pesantren Majma'al Bahroin Hubbul Wathon minal Iman Shiddiqiyyah atau Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah di Jalan Ploso-Babat, Kecamatan Ploso, Kabupaten Jombang, Jawa Timur. Izin dicabut setelah pengasuh pesantren tersebut, Kiai MM, ikut terseret kasus pencabulan yang menjerat anaknya, Moch Subchi Azal Tsani atau Mas Bechi. Untuk diketahui, Pesantren Shiddqiyyah menjalankan lembaga pendidikan formal dan nonformal sebagaimana pesantren pada umumnya. Para murid kebanyakan adalah santri yang menetap di asrama. Selain itu, Pengasuh Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, Kiai MM, juga memiliki jemaah tarekat yang kebanyakan tidak menetap. Tarekat tersebut bernama Tarekat Shiddiqiyyah dengan Kiai MM sebagai mursyidnya.|Kepala Bidang Pendidikan Diniyah Pondok Pesantren pada Kantor Wilayah Kementerian Agama Jawa Timur, Asâ€™adul Anam, menjelaskan, karena izinnya dicabut, segala aktivitas pendidikan di Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah tidak boleh beroperasi. Pihak yayasan pesantren baru bisa mengajukan izin operasional lagi setelah dua sampai tiga tahun kemudian dan baru bisa beroperasi lagi setelah disetujui, â€œItu kalau pihak pesantren mengajukan [izin operasional lagi],â€ kata Asâ€™adul kepada wartawan di kantor Kemenag Jatim di Jalan Raya Juanda, Sedati, Kabupaten Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur, pada Jumat, 8 Juli 2022. Kegiatan yang tidak boleh beroperasi ialah kegiatan belajar mengajar, baik formal maupun nonformal. Sementara kegiatan jemaah tarekat yang dipimpin oleh Kiai MM tetap boleh beroperasi, karena hal itu bukan bagian dari kegiatan pesantren. â€œArtinya kiai [MM] masih bisa menjalankan aktivitas tarekatnya,â€ ujar Asâ€™adul. Lantas bagaimana kelanjutan pendidikan para santri Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah? â€œPara santri-santrinya ini difasilitasi untuk melanjutkan [pendidikan] kemana,â€ kata Asâ€™adul.Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah yang diasuh Kiai MM jadi sorotan setelah terserempet kasus dugaan pencabulan yang dilakukan oleh anak dari Kiai MM, Mas Sebchi. Publik menyorot karena alotnya penangkapan Mas Bechi yang sudah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka dan berstatus buronan. Kepolisian bahkan mengerahkan ratusan personel untuk menjemput paksa Mas Bechi yang sembunyi di area Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah pada Kamis kemarin. Dia akhirnya menyerahkan diri pada Kamis malam sekira pukul 23.00 WIB. Dia langsung diserahkan ke Jaksa Penuntut Umum dan ditahan di Rutan Klas I Surabaya di Medaeng, Sidoarjo.|Saksikan live streaming tvOne hanya di https://www.tvonenews.com/live

title: WARRIORS vs KNICKS | NBA SUMMER LEAGUE | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS
description: The New York Knicks defeated the Golden State Warriors, 101-88. Quentin Grimes led the way for the Knicks with 24 PTS, 4 REB and 8 AST, while Jericho Sims added 16 PTS (7-8 FG) and 10 REB in the victory. Moses Moody led all scorers with 34 PTS for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Knicks improve to 1-0 in the NBA 2K23 Summer League, while the Warriors fall to 0-1.|Stay up-to-date on news, live scores and stats with the NBA App:https://app.link.nba.com/-App22

title: Brooks and Capehart on gun violence and abortion access
description: New York Times columnist David Brooks and Washington Post associate editor Jonathan Capehart join Judy Woodruff to discuss the week in politics, including the mass shooting in a Chicago suburb and gun violence in the United States and President Biden's executive order on abortion access and the potential for legislative action after the Supreme Court reversed Roe v. title: 6th Pick Bennedict Mathurin Drops 23 PTS In Pacers Summer League Debut!
description: The Indiana Pacers defeated the Charlotte Hornets, 96-84. Bennedict Mathurin, the No. 6 overall pick in the 2022 NBA Draft out of the University of Arizona, led the way for the Pacers with a game-high 23 PTS, while Chris Duarte added 16 PTS and 4 AST in the victory. Bryce McGowens tallied 17 PTS, 6 REB and 5 AST for the Hornets, while Mark Williams added 5 PTS, 8 REB and 2 BLK in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 1-0 in the NBA 2K23 Summer League, while the Hornets fall to 0-1.|Stay up-to-date on news, live scores and stats with the NBA App:https://app.link.nba.com/-App22

title: Mantan Presiden ACT Ahyudin Diperiksa Bareskrim Polri Selama 11 Jam
description: KOMPAS.TV - Mantan presiden aksi cepat tanggap ACT Ahyudin selesai diperiksa di Bareskrim Polri pada Jumat malam. Ahyudin dicecar pertanyaan terkait legalitas yayasan ACT.||||Ahyudin keluar setelah sekitar sebelas jam diperiksa penyidik dalam kasus dugaan penyelewengan dana sumbangan yayasan ACT. Ahyudin diperiksa dalam kapasitasnya sebagai saksi.||||Baca Juga Diperiksa 12 Jam Mantan Presiden ACT Ahyudin Ngaku Tak Ditanya soal Keuangan dan Aliran Dana di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307285/diperiksa-12-jam-mantan-presiden-act-ahyudin-ngaku-tak-ditanya-soal-keuangan-dan-aliran-dana||||Ada 22 pertanyaan semuanya menurut Ahyudin terkait legalitas yayasan.||||Belum ada dokumen yang dibawa Ahyudin dan kuasa hukum dan pemeriksaan rencananya dilanjut senin pekan depan.||||Dalam perkara ini, ACT diduga melakukan penyelewengan dana sumbangan untuk memperkaya para pengurus hingga mengalir ke luar negeri.||||Selain mantan presiden ACT Ahyudin presiden ACT Ibnu Khajar juga diperiksa penyidik Bareskrim Polri.||||Tak ada komentar yang disampaikan Ibnu Khajar, menurut informasi polisi selain Ibnu dan Ahyudin polisi juga menjadwalkan pemeriksaan terhadap manajer proyek dan bagian keuangan di ACT.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307313/mantan-presiden-act-ahyudin-diperiksa-bareskrim-polri-selama-11-jam

title: Muhammadiyah Tetapkan Hari Raya Idul Adha pada 9 Juli
description: KOMPAS.TV - Muhammadiyah menetapkan hari raya Idul Adha 1443 H pada 9 Juli 2022. Jemaah di Jeneponto, Sulawesi Selatan pun bersiap untuk pelaksanaan shalat Idhul Adha pada pagi ini.||||Pelaksaan shalat Idul Adha akan dilakukan di pelataran kantor Muhammadiyah Jeneponto pukul 7 WITA.||||Baca Juga Jelang Hari Raya Idul Adha, Stasiun Rangkasbitung Dipadati Penumpang di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307289/jelang-hari-raya-idul-adha-stasiun-rangkasbitung-dipadati-penumpang||||Sejumlah persiapan telah di lakukan pada Jumat malam di antaranya memepersiapkan alas untuk salat sebagai penanda shaf untuk jemaah.||||Ketua Umum PP Muhammadiyah Haedar Nashir mengajak seluruh umat muslim untuk hidup rukun dan saling menghargai perbedaan termasuk dalam perbedaan dalam perayaan Idul Adha.||||Jakarta Internasional Stadium atau JIS dipastikan kembali menjadi lokasi utama penyelenggaraan Shalat Idul Adha di ibu kota.||||Hal itu diungkapkan Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan saat ditemui di Balai Kota DKI Jakarta pada Jumat sore.||||Masyarakat dapat mengikuti shalat Idul Adha di JIS yang akan dimulai pada pukul 6.30 Minggu pagi besok.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307295/muhammadiyah-tetapkan-hari-raya-idul-adha-pada-9-juli
tags: idul adha|jakarta internasional stadium|jis|muhammadiyah|shalat idul adha

The Barbasol Championship provides the final opportunity for players to qualify for The Open Championship via The Open Qualifying Series. The event offers one exemption to the leading player (not otherwise exempt) who finishes in the top five and ties. In last yearâ€™s edition, held on the same week as The Open, Irelandâ€™s Seamus Power won his first PGA TOUR title following a six-hole play-off against J.T. Poston. This year, Matti Schmid is one of the DP World Tour members in the field and his appearance sees him return to the state of Kentucky, where he played college golf at the University of Louisville. The Germanâ€™s amateur career included back-to-back wins in the European Amateur in 2019 and 2020 and the Silver Medal as the low amateur in last yearâ€™s The Open at Royal St Georgeâ€™s. title: Someone Edited Obi-Wan Kenobi Into a Two and a Half Hour Movie - IGN Daily Fix
description: In today's Fix of entertainment news, you can now rewatch Disney+'s Obi-Wan Kenobi Series, but in a relatively tight two-and-a-half hours. A fan recut the 6-episode series into a feature-length movie for his own enjoyment and put it up online for others. Sorry, we're not going to tell you how to find it (but you can probably figure that out on your own). In Netflix news, the streaming giant is tryingâ€”for the second timeâ€”to make a live-action Death note. This time it will be produced by the Duffer Brothers of Stranger Things fame. The last time Netflix made a live-action adaptation of the manga/anime, it didn't go so well. Second time's a charm, maybe. And sticking with Netflix, your movies and shows may just get a little more immersive as the company is enabling spatial audio for some of its original series and films. The tech will be provided by Sennheiser using their AMBEO technology. How do you watch your movies at home? Surround sound system? Sound Bar? Headphones? A good ol' fashioned pair of laptop speakers? Let us know in the comments!||||#IGN #StarWars

title: Global National: July 8, 2022 | Rogers outage affects millions across Canada
description: In our top story: People and businesses across Canada were forced to deal with Rogers Communications getting knocked offline, which impacted everything from cellphone service to internet connections and banking services. The big question causing headaches for millions is how Rogers has responded so far. Abigail Bimman reports.|Japan is reeling after former prime minister Shinzo Abe was shot and killed at a campaign event in the western city of Nara. Crystal Goomansingh reports on the investigation into the suspected gunman, and the tributes pouring in for Abe.|In the U.S., exactly two weeks after the Supreme Court overturned Roe v. Wade, President Joe Biden has signed an executive order aimed at safeguarding abortion rights for American women. Jackson Proskow reports on why his options are limited, and the criticism he's facing.|Plus, the story of a Russian soldier who died fighting in Ukraine, and the revelations about who many of these troops are and why they enlisted. Jeff Semple has an exclusive look, with the investigation revealing how many troops are from poor, ethnic minority groups.|And back in the saddle: for the first time since the pandemic began, the Calgary Stampede has kicked off without COVID-19 restrictions. But as Heather Yourex-West explains, the 10-day event, billed as the "greatest outdoor show on Earth," is experiencing some pandemic-caused problems.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #GlobalNational #RogersOutage

title: Ukrainian troops dig in to stop Russian advance on the Donbas
description: In the Donetsk region, Ukrainian soldiers could hear the booms of artillery fire nearby on Friday as they began to hunker down and prepare to defend a new front line in the fight for the Donbas region, with several taking up positions near the city of Siversk.|Russian President Vladimir Putin has made capturing the industrialized region the principal war aim after aborting an assault on Kyiv that began on Feb. 24, when the invasion of Ukraine began.|While some of the soldiers have been utilizing foreign-made weapons, there is concern the current commitments of long-range weapons and ammunition may not be enough but they are hopeful they will be able to push Russian forces back.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8977207/us-military-aid-ukraine-russia-war/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews

title: HIGHLIGHTS | Nurnberg v Arsenal (3-5) | Jesus (2), Elneny
description: New signing Gabriel Jesus scored 90 seconds into his non-competitive debut to trigger an extraordinary turnaround in Germany.|1. FC Nurnberg, who play in the second tier of German football, raced to a 2-0 half-time lead, before we emerged as a different proposition after the break.|Jesus had to sit and watch from the bench for the opening half, alongside other new arrival Marquinhos, with Matt Turner the only one of our four summer signings named in the starting XI.|But once Jesus was unleashed, he marked the occasion with a wonderful brace, and had a say in both of the own goals too.|The other goal came from the boot of Mohamed Elneny, and what a screamer it was, flying in from long range.|Mikel Arteta opted for a fairly young starting lineup, including 17-year-old defender Reuell Walters, one of several youngsters out with the squad at our training camp in Germany.|He started in the centre of defence alongside Pablo Mari, and showed his speed early on to get back and dispossess Kwadwo Duah. Christoph Daferner had already headed wide when well placed in a bright opening for the home side.|It look 15 minutes for us to fashion our first effort on goal. Emile Smith Roweâ€™s right-footed curler was goalbound until Christian Mathenia in the hostsâ€™ goal turned it away for a corner.|Midway through the half though we fell behind, when Johannes Geis struck powerfully from outside the area, in off the crossbar. There was plenty of pace and movement on the shot, deceiving Turner in the Gunners goal.|Just five minutes later Duah doubled the advantage, cracking home across Turner inside the far post after we lost possession cheaply.|We had to regroup. Ainsley Maitland-Niles flashed a cross-shot just wide while Reiss Nelson saw an effort deflected behind for a corner.|But we failed to really get going in the opening half, and went in two goals down at the break.|Jesus was brought on at the interval, along with three other subs. And with virtually his first touch in an Arsenal shirt, he fired us back into the game.|He picked up possession outside the area, advanced and swapped passes with Eddie Nketiah, before smashing home at the near post. What an introduction to life as a Gunner.|The tone of the game had changed and moments later he strode into the box again before being tackled this time.|One of the other half-time replacements, Mohamed Elneny, brought us level with an absolute thunderbolt from fully 25 yards.|Inside an hour we were ahead. After another excellent move, a deep cross was destined for Jesusâ€™s head, only for Christopher Schindler to stretch out a boot and turn the ball past his own keeper.|It was a stunning 12-minute turnaround from Artetaâ€™s men.|We werenâ€™t finished there though. Just after the hour mark, Nketiahâ€™s shot cannoned back off the cross bar, hit Nurnberg defender Tim Handwerker and trickled over his own goal-line under pressure from Jesus.|More subs followed for the last 20 minutes, with Folarin Balogun, Charlie Patino, Salah Oulad Mâ€™hand, Arthur Okonkwo and new arrival Marquinhos all coming on.|Nurnberg substitute Lukas Schleimer momentarily pulled it back to a single goal deficit, but Jesus soon claimed his second of the afternoon, from a Gabriel Martinelli cross, to make it 5-3.|It was a wonderful, instinctive finish from our new boy to beat the keeper from close range.|By now we were in control, and able to enjoy the denouement to a week of hard work and preparation at the adidas HQ in Germany. title: Highlights | Round 2 | Genesis Scottish Open | 2022
description: Check out the best shots of the day from round 2 of the 2022 Genesis Scottish Open, featuring Cameron Tringale who leads the field by three strokes, currently sitting at 7-under for the tournament.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the best players on the PGA TOUR and the DP World Tour will compete against one another in the first co-sanctioned Genesis Scottish Open between the two tours. Players from each tour will be teeing it up at The Renaissance Club in North Berwick, including 2022 Travelers Champion Xander Schauffele, 2022 PGA Championship winner Justin Thomas, World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler and former World No. 1 John Rahm. U.S. Open Champion Matt Fitzpatrick will make his much-anticipated return at the Genesis Scottish Open and will be looking to build on his result last year, when he finished runner-up to Min Woo Lee, who defeated Fitzpatrick and Thomas Detry in a three-way playoff. Robert MacIntyre will be carrying the hopes of the home fans as the highest-ranked Scottish player in the field, while the top-ranked player on the DP World Tour, Will Zalatoris, who finished runner up at both the U.S. Open and the PGA Championship, will be hoping to turn his excellent form into his first win on either tour. ||||Welcome to the official YouTube channel of the PGA TOUR. Here you can find everything you need to stay up to date with the worldâ€™s foremost golf tour. title: Jordan Spieth battles windy conditions | Round 2 highlights | 2022 Genesis Scottish Open
description: Jordan Spieth was one of a number of afternoon starters who battled blustery conditions as he reached the halfway stage of the 2022 Genesis Scottish Open at level par. He's currently T20.|â–º SUBSCRIBE: http://et.golf/Subscribe ||||The Rolex Series returns to the DP World Tour this week as a stellar field assembles at The Renaissance Club for the Genesis Scottish Open. All four reigning Major Champions and 14 of the top 15 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are teeing it up in East Lothian, with the event co-sanctioned by the PGA TOUR. Spaniard Jon Rahm is a two-time winner of Ireland's national open and also finished third at The 2021 Open Championship and seventh at this event last season. Add all that to his recent win at the Mexico Open at Vidanta and five other top tens this season and the 2019 European Number One looks a tough man to beat. If anyone is to beat Rahm, it may well be World Number One Scottie Scheffler, a man still enjoying the run of form that catapulted him to the top of the Official World Golf Ranking. The 26-year-old claimed wins at WM Phoenix Open, Arnold Palmer Invitational and WGC-Dell Technologies Match Play before his maiden Major Championship victory at the Masters Tournament, his fourth win in six events. Other names to look out for include the likes of Patrick Cantly, Justin Thomas, Viktor Hovland, Cameron Smith, Collin Morikawa, Hideki Matsuyama and Matt Fitzpatrick.||||Welcome to the Official YouTube channel of the DP World Tour. title: Gov. Abbott issues executive order apprehend illegal immigrants and return them to the border.
description: On Thursday, Gov. Greg Abbott issued an executive order that authorizes the Texas National Guard and the Texas Department of Public Safety to apprehend immigrants in the country illegally and return them to the border.|In a press release announcing the new order, Gov. Abbott blamed the Biden Administration's recent decision to end Title 42 expulsions and the "remain in Mexico" policy for "historic levels of illegal crossings." Abbott's office said 5,000 migrants were apprehended over the Fourth of July weekend and that there is an ongoing crisis that has "overrun communities" at the border and across the state.|"While President Biden refuses to do his job and enforce the immigration laws enacted by Congress, the State of Texas is once again stepping up and taking unprecedented action to protect Americans and secure our southern border," said Gov. Abbott. "The cartels have become emboldened and enriched by President Biden's open border policies, smuggling in record numbers of people, weapons and deadly drugs like fentanyl."

title: Remembering the life and legacy of Japan's former Prime Minister Shinzo Abe
description: Authorities in Japan said a 41-year-old man who formerly served in the Japanese Navy was responsible for the death of former Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, who was shot dead with a homemade gun in a nation that has largely eliminated gun violence. title: Baker Mayfield-Browns reportedly figuring out what went wrong, Kevin Stefanski | NFL | THE HERD
description: Baker Mayfield is the Carolina Panthers' newest QB after the Cleveland Browns traded the former No. 1 pick for a 2024 conditional fifth round pick that could turn into a fourth rounder. According to The Athletic, Baker and the Browns are reportedly attempting to figure out what went wrong between both parties. In addition, a lack of trust reportedly soured between the QB and Browns Head Coach Kevin Stefanski. Baker's shoulder injury did not help his final season in Cleveland but his low fourth quarter numbers stood out throughout his career. title: What happens if Russia cuts off gas supplies to Europe? | DW Business Special
description: Perhaps the most important piece of gas infrastructure in Europe is being switched off on July 11. Russia will turn off the taps of the Nord Stream 1 pipeline for 10 days, which it says is necessary to carry out maintenance. title: Painting My Tie Dye (AGAIN.)
description: Hey guys! Today I am combining 2 of my favorite art activities: tie dye and painting/customizing clothes. SO. I am going to be tie dying the clothing using Tulip's new 2 minute tie dye kit. I basically tested this kit and gave a mini review of it in my last tie dye video in case you are interested in that. AND THEN I painted on the tie dyed clothing. In the end I have completely customized clothing using some of my original characters and designs. This was SO much fun, it was a really easy and enjoyable art project to do with common supplies. I definitely recommend trying this out if you are looking for a fun and creative DIY art or craft project. You could even do this as a way to repurpose thrifted clothing and do aa little outfit makeover!|___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________|Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh ğŸ˜‚ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 26 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. title: Putin warns sanctions on Russia â€œcatastrophicâ€ for global energy market, European households
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin warned on Friday that continued sanctions against Russia could lead to â€œcatastrophicâ€ energy price rises for European households, claiming that sanction restrictions cause more damage to imposing countries than on Russia.| |â€œFurther use of sanctions may lead to even more severe â€” without exaggeration, even catastrophic â€” consequences on the global energy market," Putin said at a televised meeting with senior officials.| |"I see certain colleagues [thinking]... we do not give a damn about those sanctions, to hell with them,â€ he added, urging caution from the Russian side as well. â€œYes, we must feel confident, but we must recognize the risks, too."| |Europe has historically relied on Russia for around 40 per cent of its natural gas, with most of it delivered through pipelines. European gas prices soared in 2021 as supply failed to keep pace with demand driven by a recovery from the coronavirus pandemic, and leaping again since Russia sent troops into Ukraine.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8975074/ukraine-russia-putin-speech-warning/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #Russia #Energy

title: Momen Prabowo Disambut TNI Angkatan Udara di Langit Iswahjudi: I
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota. https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||MADIUN, KOMPAS.TV -  Menteri Pertahanan RI Prabowo Subianto mendapatkan sambutan hangat dari para TNI AU di langit IswahJudi. ||||"Mohon Izin kepada yang terhormat Menteri Pertahanan Bapak Prabowo Subianto, kami anak-anak muda mengucapkan selamat pagi, dan selamat datang kepada bapak Prabowo Suianto di wilayah langit Iswahjudi"bunyi sambutan itu. ||||Prabowo pun mengaku terharu dan bangga pada TNI AU Iswahjudi. ||||"Saya mau bikin pengakuan mtadi saya pakai kacamata gelap, lihat angaktan udara saya, saya bangga dengan kalian,"kata Prabowo menanggapi sambutan itu. ||||Baca Juga Saat Megawati Kaget Prabowo Beri Hormat di HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306018/saat-megawati-kaget-prabowo-beri-hormat-di-hut-ke-76-bhayangkara||||Serangkaian kunjungan kerja (kunker) ke Madiun, Jawa Timur, Jumat (8/7/2022), diawali peninjauan ke Pangkalan TNI Angkatan Udara Iswahjudi. ||||Dalam kesempatan tersebut Prabowoingin TNI AU unggul dan kuat. ||||"Koopsudnas juga harus kuat menjaga wilayah yang sangat luas. Saya berbuat semaksimal mungkin membangun Angkatan Udara supaya kuat dan menjadi kebanggaan seluruh bangsa", tegas Prabowo dalam sambutannya.||||Prabowo pun menerima paparan tentang tugas pokok dan fungsi serta kesiapan Lanud Iswahjudi khususnya dalam pembinaan personel dan pengoperasian alutsista matra udara, serta meninjau hangar pesawat static show T50, F16 dan Shukoi SU-30 di Skadron 14.||||Video Editor: Galih|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307248/momen-prabowo-disambut-tni-angkatan-udara-di-langit-iswahjudi-i

title: FIRST DRIVE: Audi RS Q e-tron - Electric Dakar Car Tested On and Off-Road | Top Gear
description: This is the Audi RS Q e-tron - the most interesting racing car of 2022. Back in January, it competed in its first-ever raceÂ â€“ the biggest, most grueling, most hostile event on the planet: the Dakar rally. It was the first electrically-powered car to do so, and it was instantly on the pace, the three cars recording four stage wins between them. It uses an electric motor from a Formula E car on each axle, drawing power from a 50kWh battery pack underneath the seats. We know what youâ€™re thinking - 50kWh is pretty average by todayâ€™s EV standards, especially considering this had to cover 8000kms of Saudi Arabian desert. Good thing it carries its own charger, in the form of a 2.0L turbocharged DTM engine from an old RS5.|Since Dakar cars are road-legal, we sent Top Gear Magazineâ€™s Ollie Marriage to find out what the 2.3-metre wide racer is like to drive around town, before testing it in a slightly more suitable off-road location.|Chapters|0:00 Intro|0:37 Q+A with Carlos Sainz Sr. |3:17 Road Driving|6:03 Off-Road driving|9:00 Highlights + Features |10:24 Party Trick|10:52 Outro|Subscribe to Top Gear for more videos: http://bit.ly/SubscribeToTopGear|MORE ABOUT TOP GEAR:|Want to watch a bit of Top Gear on the internet? title: 'Will crush...': China flies military jets as U.S delegation arrives in Taiwan for 3-day visit
description: Fresh China vs United States tension after Republican Senator Rick Scott arrived in Taiwan on a 3-day visit. China conducted military drills and flew fighter jets near Taiwan in response to the visit.Beijing in a statement by Eastern Theater Command accused Washington of making repeated moves of supporting 'Taiwan Independence'. It further stated that any attempts of 'Taiwan Independence' will be crushed as it is the  part of mainland China. Rick Scott arrived in Taipei and met President Tsai Ing-Wen and said that the island nation has all the right to decide its future. Watch this video to know more.|#china #taiwan #usa #PLA #beijing #joebiden #taiwanstrait #xijinping

title: Hole-In-One Wins Genesis Cars for Player and Caddie | 2022 Genesis Scottish Open
description: Jordan Smith bagged himself and his caddie a brand new Genesis car each after firing a hole-in-one on the 17th during the second round of the 2022 Genesis Scottish Open. But he was not the only one heading into the clubhouse with a new set of car keys as his caddie Sam Matton wins a new all-electric Genesis GV60.|â–º SUBSCRIBE: http://et.golf/Subscribe ||||The Rolex Series returns to the DP World Tour this week as a stellar field assembles at The Renaissance Club for the Genesis Scottish Open. All four reigning Major Champions and 14 of the top 15 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are teeing it up in East Lothian, with the event co-sanctioned by the PGA TOUR. Spaniard Jon Rahm is a two-time winner of Ireland's national open and also finished third at The 2021 Open Championship and seventh at this event last season. Add all that to his recent win at the Mexico Open at Vidanta and five other top tens this season and the 2019 European Number One looks a tough man to beat. If anyone is to beat Rahm, it may well be World Number One Scottie Scheffler, a man still enjoying the run of form that catapulted him to the top of the Official World Golf Ranking. The 26-year-old claimed wins at WM Phoenix Open, Arnold Palmer Invitational and WGC-Dell Technologies Match Play before his maiden Major Championship victory at the Masters Tournament, his fourth win in six events. Other names to look out for include the likes of Patrick Cantly, Justin Thomas, Viktor Hovland, Cameron Smith, Collin Morikawa, Hideki Matsuyama and Matt Fitzpatrick.||||Welcome to the Official YouTube channel of the DP World Tour. Every week you can find extended tournament highlights and individual player highlights from the likes of Rory McIlroy, Justin Rose and Tommy Fleetwood. This is also the home of the 14 Club Challenge, Little Interviews, Fastest Hole and many more challenges, pranks and world record attempts featuring the biggest golfers in the world. ||||â–º WEBSITE: http://www.europeantour.com||â–º FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/DPWorldTour||â–º TWITTER https://twitter.com/DPWorldTour||â–º INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/dpworldtour/

title: Kevin Durant's market, LeBron reportedly pushing for a Kyrie Irving reunion in LA | NBA | THE HERD
description: The Brooklyn Nets are looking to trade Kevin Durant (via request) and Kyrie Irving. However, according to Brian Windhorst, the Nets have not received the 'bidding war' they expected. KD is arguably an all-time great but is 33 years old with four years remaining on his contract, making it difficult to find trade suitors. Colin Cowherd evaluates what this says about KD. On the west coast, Windhorst also reported that LeBron James wants Kyrie more than the Los Angeles Lakers do and is not considering their future draft picks. LeBron's time in the league is ending soon but should the Lakers proceed with LeBron's request? title: Trump's ex-White House counsel testifies to Jan. 6 committee
description: The House select committee investigating the January 6, 2021, insurrection is expected to ask Trump White House Counsel Pat Cipollone during a closed-door interview about what he witnessed in the waning days of Donald Trump's administration when the former President and his allies tried to overturn the election. The interview is being recorded on video and could be featured at upcoming hearings, including one about how the violent mob came together and the role of extremist groups, as well as another hearing on the 187 minutes of Trump's inaction as rioters stormed the US Capitol. #CNN #News

title: Kemenang Cabut Izin Ponpes Shiddiqiyyah, PWNU Jatim : Jangan Ada Kesan Pesantren Ajarkan Pelecehan
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Tersangka pencabulan santriwati, Muhammad Subchi Azal Tsani alias Bechi ditahan.||||Tersangka akhirnya diserahkan Polda Jatim ke Kejaksaan Tinggi Jawa Timur.||||Tersangka kasus pencabulan santriwati di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah Jombang, Bechi langsung ditahan di Rumah Tahanan Kelas I Surabaya Medaeng Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur, setelah menyerahkan diri kepada penyidik Polda Jatim, Kamis (7/07) malam.||||Bechi ditahan di Rutan Kelas I Surabaya di Medaeng Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur.||||Baca Juga Bechi Ditetapkan Sebagai Tersangka Sejak 2020, Ada 5 Laporan Terkait Kasus Pencabulan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307198/bechi-ditetapkan-sebagai-tersangka-sejak-2020-ada-5-laporan-terkait-kasus-pencabulan||||Penyidik Polda Jawa Timur resmi melimpahkan kasus pencabulan dengan tersangka Bechi ke Kejaksaan Tinggi Jawa Timur untuk disidangkan.||||Proses pelimpahan tersangka dan barang bukti dilakukan di Rutan I Surabaya, Rutan Medaeng pada Jumat (8/08) siang dengan menghadirkan tersangka, Mochamad subhi azal tsani.||||Sementara itu, pihak kantor wilayah Kementerian Agama Provinsi Jawa Timur, akhirnya secara resmi mencabut izin operasional, Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, Kecamatan Ploso, Jombang, Jawa Timur.||||Meski demikian Kanwil Kemenag Jatim akan tetap memfasilitasi, para santri yang hingga kini masih berada di ponpes itu.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307256/kemenang-cabut-izin-ponpes-shiddiqiyyah-pwnu-jatim-jangan-ada-kesan-pesantren-ajarkan-pelecehan

description: A Chinese Air Force aircraft flew very close to a friction point in the eastern Ladakh sector on the Line of Actual Control in the last week of June, after which the Indian Air Force responded swiftly as per standard operating procedures. The incident took place at around 4 am on one of the days in the last week of June and after the aircraft was spotted by men on ground and was also picked up by indigenous radars deployed in the border area, sources said. title: Akhirnya, Dokter Terawan Menjawab | Rosi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dokter Terawan Agus Putranto akhirnya bicara. Secara eksklusif, Dokter Terawan menjawab sejumlah pertanyaan publik kepada Rosianna Silalahi. |Sosok Dokter Terawan tak lepas dari kontroversi. Ia dinilai melanggar etik, karena metode cuci otaknya yang belum teruji klinis. Tak hanya itu, Dokter Terawan melanjutkan terobosannya lewat Vaksin Nusantara. Mengapa Dokter Terawan begitu berani? |Simak wawancara eksklusif tanpa cut Rosianna Silalahi bersama Prof. Dr. dr. Terawan Agus Putranto, SpRad (K) dalam ROSI Eps. "Akhirnya, Dokter Terawan Menjawab" malam ini Jumat, 8 Juli pukul 19.00 WIB hanya di KompasTV, Independen Terpercaya. |Timestamps: |00:00:19 Bumper In |00:00:20 Filler |00:01:43 Apa kabar, Dokter Terawan? |00:04:56 Mengapa akhirnya Dokter Terawan mau diwawancarai Rosianna Silalahi? |00:07:28 Dokter Terawan menjawab polemik pernyataannya soal warga yang membeli masker di masa tanggap darurat pandemi Covid-19 |00:13:55 Apakah Dokter Terawan merasa gagal menjadi Menteri Kesehatan?|00:17:05 Penuh kontroversi, apakah Dokter Terawan memang selalu cari gara-gara? |00:19:53 Dokter Terawan: â€œVaksin Nusantara sudah diuji klinis oleh sayaâ€|00:21:15 Dokter Terawan: â€œKalau uji klinis itu dijadikan halangan, kapan kita mau investasi?â€ |00:23:50 Mengapa Dokter Terawan tidak menjalankan prosedur sesuai BPOM? |00:27:40 Apakah Dokter Terawan merasa selama ini risetnya dihalangi demi kemajuan medis di Indonesia? |00:32:43 Betulkah Vaksin Nusantara 100 persen karya anak bangsa? Dokter Terawan menjawab |00:36:07 Dokter Terawan: â€œSaya sudah berkali-kali dipecat (oleh IDI), jadi biasa saja.â€ |00:40:04 Dokter Terawan: â€œSaya pernah datang ke MKEK, lalu ini yang terjadiâ€¦â€ |00:44:56 Dokter Terawan: â€œYang menentukan benar atau salah bukan sebuah organisasi, tapi kolegium kedokteran.â€ |00:49:40 Dokter Terawan: â€œMemangnya IDI segalanya? Kalau masuk akal, saya ikutiâ€ |00:53:43 Apakah Dokter Terawan tidak ingin mengikuti rekomendasi IDI? |00:57:03 Dokter Terawan: â€œAlasan medis yang tidak masuk akal, tidak boleh diikuti. Saya tegas untuk itu.â€ |00:58:12 Apakah para dokter masih memerlukan organisasi kesehatan seperti IDI? |00:01:20 benarkah keberanian Dokter Terawan karena di-backing oleh jenderal dan elite politik? |Jangan lewatkan dialog seru lainnya di program ROSI setiap hari Kamis pukul 20.30 WIB hanya di @kompastv, Independen Terpercaya.|Follow akun ROSI:|Instagram: @rosi_kompastv|Twitter: RosiKompasTV|Tiktok: Rosi_KompasTV|#DokterTerawan #VaksinNusantara #TerapiCuciOtak #RosiKompasTV #KompasTV #Talkshow

title: G20 summit in Bali overshadowed by Ukraine war | DW News
description: The foreign ministers of the Group of 20 (G20) countries are attending a joint summit on Friday on the Indonesian island of Bali, amid tensions between the West and Russia over Ukraine.|Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov was in attendance despite objections from Western leaders. However, he left early and walked out of a morning session as German Foreign Minister Annalena Baerbock criticized Moscow over its invasion of Ukraine.|"The fact that the Russian foreign minister spent a large part of the negotiations here not in the room but outside the room underlines that there is not even a millimeter of willingness to talk on the part of the Russian government at the moment," Baerbock said.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#g20 #ukrainewar #indonesia

title: Thor: Love & Thunder Post-Credits, Ending Explained & Easter Eggs | Marvel Canon Fodder
description: he God of Thunder rides again in Thor: Love and Thunder, the fourth solo film for the character and his first in the post-Endgame MCU Phase 4. Thor and his pal Korg are investigating Gorr the God Butcher with the help of Valkyrie and The Mighty Thor, a.k.a. Dr. Jane Foster. Join IGN host Max Scoville or Canon Fodder for the full breakdown, ending explained and all the Easter Eggs we could find. ||||Thor: Love and Thunder aka Thor 4 takes the funniest and possible strongest Avenger on a new adventure and phase of his life! Thor (Chris Hemsworth) takes the lead in Love and Thunder alongside Jane (Natalie Portman) to take on Gorr the God Butcher (Christian Bale). It's been a long time in Marvel history without Dr. Jane Foster, and we find out what she's been up to and how she's come to wear the winged helm in Taika Waititi's second Thor film. How do the Guardians of the Galaxy come into play, and how is the MCU handling Mighty Thor? Are Korg and Valkyrie (Tessa Thompson) going to survive the movie? How did Mjolnir switch owners? Is Star-Lord (Chris Pratt) totally taken over by that Thor charisma?? Don't worry, we've got all the answers. Jane Foster's so-called "Lady Thor" teams up with King Valkyrie while Thor finishes a Classic Thor Adventure, leaving more than one loose end for Guardians of the Galaxy 3 to worry about. Meanwhile, there's more to the Jane Foster/Thor relationship that was left out of the solo films and Avengers movies from Marvel Studios. We also get possibly the scariest Marvel villain yet in Gorr the God Butcher and something you might not see coming for the ending. Explained in the comics but perhaps not on screen, we're going to breakdown everything in Marvel comics canon, along with all those lovely easter eggs, and let's not forget the Thor: Love and Thunder post credits scene, after the mid credits scene at first. Is the speculation about Hercules true? What about the repeated Valhalla mentions? And how does Brett Goldstein fit into this?|#IGN #Thor #Movies

description: This is a 1966 Mercury Montclair that's been abandoned in a barn for 26 years. The Mercury has a great story and was owned by Emmy Award Winning Screenwriter John Vlahos. A kind viewer of the channel recently bought the property and asked me to save the Mercury from the crusher. The collection of acorns in the barn was a sign of what's to come as I found the largest mouse nest I've ever seen during the detail. One of the most challenging and intensive clean-ups for sure but all worth it to donate the Mercury to a generous subscriber. title: Detik Detik Polisi Tangkap MSAT Hingga Ricuh
description: Inilah detik detik penangkapan MSAT, anak Kiai Haji Muhktar Mukhti asal Jombang yang menjadi tersangka kasus dugaan pencabulan santriwati.|Drama penangkapan MSAT alias Mas Bechi, akhirnya berakhir pada Kamis, sekitar pukul 11 malam.|Mas Bechi, anak seorang Kiai dari Jombang, yang juga Wakil Rektor Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyya,  sebelumnya menjadi buron, setelah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka kasus dugaan pencabulan santriwati sejak 2020 oleh Polda Jawa Timur.|Kapolda Jatim, Irjen Nico Afinta menyatakan, proses penangkapan Mas Bechi berlangsung alot, karena polisi mengedepankan upaya pendekatan humanis.

title: PM Modi's emotional tribute to 'dear friend' Shinzo Abe; India declares one-day national mourning
description: Condoling the demise of his "dear friend" Shinzo Abe, Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Friday said the former Japanese premier dedicated his life to making the world a better place and as a mark of India's deepest respect, one-day national mourning shall be observed on July 9. In emotional posts on Twitter, Modi said that during his recent visit to Japan, he had the opportunity to meet Abe again and discuss many issues, but "little did I know that this would be our last meeting".|#narendramodi #shinzoabe #japan #japanese #pmmodi #shinzoabedead #indiajapan

title: Situasi Pesantren Shiddiqiyah Usai Izinnya Dicabut Kemenag
description: Kementerian Agama telah nyatakan mencabut izin Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqyyah Jombang Jawa Timur. Namun segala kegiatan untuk melayani masyarakat masih dapat berjalan. Terkait para santri yang masih menjalani proses pendidikan, Kementrian Agama Jawa Timur akan memindahkan sementara ke pondok pesantren lainnya dan menyerahkan kembali keputusan kepada orang tua santri masing masing.

title: Jaishankar discusses Ukraine conflict with Russian counterpart on the sidelines of G20 meet in Bali
description: External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar holds bilateral talks with his Russian counterpart Sergey Lavrov in Bali. The meeting took place on the sidelines of the G-20 foreign ministers' conclave in the Indonesian city. The two leaders discussed the ongoing Ukraine conflict. The Jaishankar-Lavrov talks came a week after Prime Minister Narendra Modi and Russian President Vladimir Putin discussed in a phone conversation the state of global energy and food markets in the backdrop of the Ukraine crisis. Watch this report for more details.|#jaishankar #sergeylavrov #g20 #g20summit #russia #india #indiarussiarelation #putin #vladimirputin #narendramodi #modi #ukraine #ukrainewar #russianoil #russiancrude #bali

title: BREAKING NEWS - Mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang, Shinzo Abe Ditembak Saat Tengah Berpidato!
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota. https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||JEPANG, KOMPAS.TV - Mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang, Shinzo Abe ditembak saat pidato kampanye di Jepang Barat.||||Abe terlihat pingsan dalam kondisi berdarah, dan mengalami gagal jantung.||||Kondisi Abe diungkapkan oleh televisi publik Jepang, NHK.||||Abe terjatuh, saat berpidato di kampanye jelang pemilihan hari Minggu (10/07) untuk Majelis Tinggi Parlemen.||||Saksi mata melaporkan mendengar tembakan dan Abe dibawa ke rumah sakit.||||Shinzo Abe, adalah politikus senior partai berkuasa, Partai Demokrat Liberal atau LDP.||||Baca Juga Mantan PM Jepang Shinzo Abe Dilaporkan Meninggal Dunia Usai Ditembak di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307164/mantan-pm-jepang-shinzo-abe-dilaporkan-meninggal-dunia-usai-ditembak||||Abe menjabat sebagai Perdana Menteri pada 2006 selama satu tahun, lalu sejak 2012 hingga 2020.||||Shinzo Abe resmi mengundurkan diri dari Perdana Menteri Jepang, pada 28 Agustus 2020.||||Alasan mundur dari perdana menteri, karena sakit radang usus besar yang sudah dideritanya.||||Dua bulan sebelum mengundurkan diri dari Perdana Menteri Jepang, Shinzo Abe mengumumkan penyakit radang usus besar atau kolitis ulseratif kronis, yang sudah diderita Abe sejak remaja, kambuh.||||Abe mengaku telah menjalani serangkaian pengobatan, dan ingin fokus terhadap perawatan kesehatannya.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307178/breaking-news-mantan-perdana-menteri-jepang-shinzo-abe-ditembak-saat-tengah-berpidato
tags: jepang|mantan angkatan laut jepang|perdana menteri jepang|shinzo abe|shinzo abe ditembak

title: Bechi Ditetapkan Sebagai Tersangka Sejak 2020, Ada 5 Laporan Terkait Kasus Pencabulan!
description: JOMBANG, KOMPAS.TV - Muhammad Subchi Azal Tsani alias Bechi tersangka yang masuk dalam daftar pencarian orang kasus pencabulan santri di Ponpes Jombang ini, akhirnya menyerahkan diri.||||Penangkapan bechi berjalan selama hampir 15 jam.||||Mulai dari upaya polisi menjemput tersangka sejak pukul 7 pagi, namun mendapat perlawanan dari simpatisan di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah.||||Hingga upaya polisi bernegosiasi dengan ayah Bechi, yang juga pengasuh Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, Kiai Haji Mukhtar Mu'thi, yang berjanji mengantarkan putranya langsung ke Polda Jawa Timur.||||Polisi juga menggeledah sejumlah ruangan di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah untuk mencari tersangka dan sejumlah barang bukti.||||Baca Juga Bechi Anak Kiai Jombang Kini Huni Sel Isolasi, Keluarga Masih Dilarang Besuk di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307169/bechi-anak-kiai-jombang-kini-huni-sel-isolasi-keluarga-masih-dilarang-besuk||||15 jam upaya penangkapan dilakukan, tersangka kasus pencabulan Bechi pun menyerahkan diri kepada polisi hingga dibawa Polda Jatim untuk menjalani pemeriksaan.||||Muhammad Subchi Azal Tsani ditetapkan sebagai tersangka sejak tahun 2020.||||Setidaknya ada 5 laporan kasus pencabulan dengan terlapor Muhammad Subchi Azal Tsani yang diterima polisi.||||Pihak kantor wilayah Kementerian Agama, Provinsi Jawa Timur, akhirnya secara resmi mencabut ijin operasional, Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, Kecamatan Ploso, Jombang.||||Meski demikian Kanwil Kemenag Jatim masih tetap akan memfasilitasi para santri yang hingga kini masih berada di ponpes itu.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307198/bechi-ditetapkan-sebagai-tersangka-sejak-2020-ada-5-laporan-terkait-kasus-pencabulan

title: Former Japanese PM Shinzo Abe assassinated during campaign speech
description: Former Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, a divisive arch-conservative and one of his nation's most powerful and influential figures, has died.| Former Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, a divisive arch-conservative and one of his nation's most powerful and influential figures, has died after being shot during a campaign speech Friday in western Japan, hospital officials said.|Abe, 67, was shot from behind minutes after he started his speech in Nara. He was airlifted to a hospital for emergency treatment but was not breathing and his heart had stopped. He was later pronounced dead despite emergency treatment that included massive blood transfusions, hospital officials said.|MORE: https://www.wfaa.com/article/news/nation-world/shinzo-abe-assassinated/507-7691dd2f-13f3-4705-af0c-8e1c2f1b8198

title: Former Japan prime minister Shinzo Abe dies after being shot at rally
description: Former Japanese leader Shinzo Abe died on Friday (Jul 8) after being shot while giving a campaign speech in southern Japan. He was 67. It was the first assassination of a sitting or former Japanese premier since the days of pre-war militarism in the 1930s. Michiyo Ishida reports from Tokyo. title: Shinzo Abe's shooter is Japan Navy veteran; Attacker fired two bullets with a handmade gun | Details
description: Japanese police officials have identified Shinzo Abe's attacker as Tetsuya Yamagami. The 41-year-old Yamagami is a resident of Nara city and is a former Japan Maritime Self-Defense Force member. The shooter had spent three years in the Japanese Navy until 2005. He fired two shots at Japan's longest serving PM Shinzo Abe from behind when he was leading an election campaign. The shooter tried to flee after the attack but Abe's security managed to catch him. title: Merinding! Detik-Detik Shinzo Abe Ditembak dari Belakang Saat Pidato
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah video yang viral di media sosial. Video ini menunjukkan detik-detik mantan PM Jepang Shinzo Abe ditembak.||||Terdengar suara tembakan menggelegar saat Shinzo Abe berpidato untuk kampanye pemilihan Majelis Tinggi yang akan dilangsungkan pada 10 Juli 2022.||||Mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang Shinzo Abe dilaporkan ditembak oleh orang tak dikenal saat berpidato di Nara pada Jumat, 8 Juli 2022 pagi waktu setempat.||||Shinzo Abe disebut tak sadarkan diri.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Shinzo Abe Ditembak Saat Berpidato! Sementara seorang pria disebut-sebut telah ditahan.||||Di lokasi kejadian, reporter NHK mengatakan mendengar dua kali tembakan berturut-turut saat Abe berpidato.||||Shinzo Abe dilarikan ke rumah sakit dalam kondisi tak sadarkan diri.||||Video Editor: Lintang.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307081/merinding-detik-detik-shinzo-abe-ditembak-dari-belakang-saat-pidato

description: KOMPAS.TV - Pemerintah akhirnya mencabut izin Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah di Poloso, Jombang, Jawa Timur karena menghalang halangi proses hukum terhadap tersangka kekesaran seksual Subhi yang merupakan putri sang pemilik ponpes.||||Kini semua kegiatan para santri otomatis dihentikan.||||Pasca drama penjemputan paksa tersangka kekerasan seksual terhadap santriwati di Jombang, Jawa Timur berlangsung a lot akhirnya pemerintah memutuskan mencabut izin pondok pesantren Shiddiqiyyah.||||Baca Juga Polisi Tahan Subchi Azal Tsani Tersangka Pencabulan Santri di Jombang di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307045/polisi-tahan-subchi-azal-tsani-tersangka-pencabulan-santri-di-jombang||||Keputusan ini diambil setelah adanya dugaan kasus kekerasan seksual yang dilakukan putra pemilik pondok pesantren.||||Selain itu, pihak pondok pesantren juga dinilai menghalang-halangi proses hukum terhadap tersangka kasus kekerasan seksual terhadap santriwati.||||Akhirnya kini kegiatan para santri dan semua kegiatan kepesantrenan otomatis dihentikan.||||Wakil Ketua Majelis Ulama Indonesia Anwar Abbas mengatakan, perbuatan tersangka angat tidak terpuji dan melanggar hukum.||||MUI mendesak polisi agar mengusut dan memproses kasus ini hingga tuntas.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307064/kemenag-cabut-izin-pesantren-shiddiqiyyah-semua-kegiatan-para-santri-dihentikan

title: Paper Sweet recipe in Tamil | Thin Flaky Paper Sweet | Pootharekulu Recipe in Tamil
description: In this video we will see how to make paper sweet recipe in tamil. We are going to use raw rice slurry to make thin and flaky paper like sheets and then fold them with sweet and nuts. title: Has the war in Ukraine affected Indonesia and Southeast Asia? | DW News
description: Russia's invasion of Ukraine is set to dominate a meeting of G-20 foreign ministers. The group of rich and developing nations have begun their talks on the Indonesian island of Bali. The countries involved are ones likely to feel the effects of a food and energy crisis that the war is setting off.|Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov opened his visit by holding talks with his Chinese counterpart Wang Yi. Wang is also expected to meet face to face with US Secretary of State Antony Blinken. US-China tensions remain high over Taiwan and trade disputes. China has also refused to condemn Russia's invasion of Ukraine, while the US is sending military gear and other assistance to bolster Kyiv's war effort.|Amid the tensions, Indonesian President Joko Widodo has been trying to mediate. Last week he visited both Russia and Ukraine in what he described as a "peace mission". Here's more on Indonesia's unique stance on the war in Ukraine.    |Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#G20 #Bali #Ukraine

title: BREAKING: Former Japanese PM Abe shot | DW News
description: Japan's Prime Minister Fumio Kishida said his predecessor Shinzo Abe is in a "very grave condition" after being shot on Friday during a campaign event in western Japan.|"I pray that former prime minister Abe will survive," Kishida said.|Earlier Chief Cabinet Secretary Hirokazu Matsuno confirmed the shooting and said that one man has been taken into custody. |Police said a 41-year-old man had been arrested. Local media reported the suspect had served in the navy and left Japan's Self-Defense Force in 2005. According to NHK, the suspect confessed to the police that he was unhappy with Abe and intended to kill him.|The attack has shocked a nation with some the world's strictest gun control laws. Public broadcaster NHK reported that the shooter used a homemade gun.|Journalist Sonja Blascke in Tokyo told DW that lots of people have "condemned the violence as the country is not used to events like this... title: No. 1 Pick Paolo Banchero Drops 17 Pts & 6 Ast In Summer League Debut!
description: Paolo Banchero and Jabari Smith II, the No. 1 and No. 3 pick in the 2022 NBA Draft, respectively, went head-to-head for the first time as the Magic defeated the Rockets, 91-77. title: Sosok Mas Bechi, Anak Kiai Jombang DPO Pencabulan Santri yang Serahkan Diri
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Tersangka Moch Subchi Azal Tsani (MSAT) akhirnya menyerahkan diri pada Kamis, 7 Juli 2022 pukul 23.00 WIB.||||Lalu siapa sosok MSAT alias Mas Bechi ini?||||Mas Bechi merupakan putra pengasuh Ponpes Shiddiqiyyah Ploso, Jombang, KH Muhammad Mukhtar Mukhti yang sempat menolak menyerahkan Bechi ke polisi.||||Mas Bechi menjabat sebagai Wakil Rektor Ponpes Majmaal Bachroin Hubbul Wathon Minal Iman Shiddiqiyyah.||||Baca Juga Ramai Kasus Bechi Jombang, Ketua DPR RI Puan Maharani Kecam Aksi Pencabulan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307039/ramai-kasus-bechi-jombang-ketua-dpr-ri-puan-maharani-kecam-aksi-pencabulan||||Kasus pencabulan terhadap santriwati muncul pada Desember 2019. Ia pun menjadi DPO polisi terkait kasus pencabulan santri di Jombang.||||Mas Bechi disebut memiliki keahlian dalam ilmu Metafakta atau Gendam.||||Mas Bechi diketahui kelahiran Jombang pada 20 Juni 1980.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307047/sosok-mas-bechi-anak-kiai-jombang-dpo-pencabulan-santri-yang-serahkan-diri

title: PEDRI REVEALS HIS NEW NUMBER ğŸ’¥
Potret Mas Bechi Diperiksa Kesehatan di Polda Jatim Usai Serahkan Diri
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah potret Moch Subchi Azal Tsani (MSAT) alias Mas Bechi yang merupakan DPO kasus pencabulan santri di Jombang.||||Dari foto yang beredar, Mas Bechi diperiksa kesehatannya oleh Tim Dokkes Polda Jawa Timur pada Jumat, 8 Juli 2022 dini hari pukul 00.55 WIB.||||Pemeriksaan kesehatan dilakukan sebagai prosedur sebelum dimasukkan ke dalam sel. Prosedur ini dilakukan untuk Mas Bechi dinyatakan sehat sebelum ditahan.||||Baca Juga Penampakan MSAT alias Mas Bechi Tersangka Pencabulan Santriwati usai Berhasil Dijemput Paksa di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306986/penampakan-msat-alias-mas-bechi-tersangka-pencabulan-santriwati-usai-berhasil-dijemput-paksa||||Mas Bechi sendiri akhirnya menyerahkan diri ke polisi pada Kamis, 7 Juli 2022 malam pada pukul 23.00 WIB, usai pihak kepolisian mengepung dan menjemput paksa selama 16 jam di Ponpes Shiddiqiyyah Ploso, Jombang.||||Pengepungan dan penjemputan paksa Mas Bechi di pondok pesantren tersebut dilakukan sejak Kamis, 7 Juli 2022 pagi pukul 07.00 WIB.||||Video Editor: Lintang||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307024/potret-mas-bechi-diperiksa-kesehatan-di-polda-jatim-usai-serahkan-diri

They con people for money. One day they see their old arch-enemy Kabir (Sanjay Dutt) driving a luxury Mercedes Benz, and they decide to disguise themselves to find the reason behind his success. They discover that he lives off his wife's wealth. They blackmail him into making them his business partners, but little do the four friends know, that Kabir and his wife Kamini (Mallika Sherawat) along with his sister Kiya (Kangna Ranaut) have a different agenda of their own. Kabir connects them with an investor named Bata Bhai who is also a part-time don. The four friends steal Bata Bhai's money, and the money is then stolen by Kabir and his family. Kabir leaves the country along with his partners and leaves the four friends to get killed by Bata Bhai. However, the four friends manage to track Kabir down. They make a plan to ruin Kabir's happiness and take their money back by going into disguise. Roy (in disguise as Tukya) cons Kiya by pretending to be in love with her. Adi (in disguise as Ghanta Singh) pretends to be Kabir's secretary. Soon enough, the four jokers ruin Kabir's full family and their happiness. As Kiya leaves Kabir because she thinks he had murdered her boyfriend Tukya (Roy) and Kamini thinks he was having an affair with a woman named Barbra (Boman). The four friends then gang up on Kabir, and take his money and run. However, before leaving his house, it is revealed that whilst they were robbing his money, it was all recorded. And the masterminds behind the plan are Kiya, Kamini and above all Kabir who knew the four idiots were coming for him. Kabir gives them seconds to run and calls Johnny Bonzela (J. Brandon Hill) over to get his money back. title: Eks PM Jepang Shinzo Abe Ditembak dari Belakang Saat Pidato Kampanye
description: KOMPAS.TV - Mantan Perdana Menteri Jepang Shinzo Abe ditembak saat pidato kampanye Jepang Barat.||||Abe terlihat pingsan dalam kondisi berdarah dan mengalami gagal jantung.||||Baca Juga Mantan PM Jepang Shinzo Abe Ditakutkan Tewas Usai Ditembak, Ini Pengakuan Saksi Mata di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307051/mantan-pm-jepang-shinzo-abe-ditakutkan-tewas-usai-ditembak-ini-pengakuan-saksi-mata||||Kondisi Abe diungkapkan oleh televisi publik Jepang NHK. title: India responds to Germany's criticism of Alt News Co-founder Zubair's arrest; 'Uninformed...'
description: India on Thursday trashed Germany's criticism over fact-checker Mohammed Zubair's arrest, saying the independence of the country's judiciary is well recognised and that "uninformed" comments are "unhelpful" and should be avoided. The comments by External Affairs Ministry Spokesperson Arindam Bagchi came a day after a German foreign ministry official said journalists should not be "persecuted and imprisoned" for what they say and write while referring to police action against Zubair.|#india #germany #zubair #altnews #mea #arindambagchi #factchecker #germanforeignministry

title: Boris Johnson Mundur dari PM, Rusia Justru Girang hingga Merayakannya, Sebut Badut Telah Pergi
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Pada Kamis ini (7/7/2022), Boris Johnson mengundurkan diri dari jabatannya sebagai Perdana Menteri Inggris. |Jatuhnya Johnson ini justru dirayakan oleh sejumlah politisi Rusia.|Mereka menyebut Johnson sebagai badut yang kini telah pergi. |Dikutip dari Kompas.com, Johnson mengundurkan diri setelah dirinya ditinggalkan oleh para menteri dan sebagian besar anggota parlemen Konservatif.|Hal ini lantaran serangkaian skandal yang menjeratnya. |Mengenai hal ini, sejumlah elit politik parlemen Rusia merayakan dan merasa gembira. |Mereka bahkan menyebut Johnson sebagai badut. |Disebutkan, Johnson mendapat hadiah karena mendukung dan mempersenjatai Ukraina melawan Rusia.|Sebagaimana diketahui, Johnson dan negara-negara sekutu Barat amat getol mengecam Rusia yang melancarkan operasi khusus militer ke Ukraina. |Bahkan paket sanksi turut dijatuhkan terhadap Moskwa. |Ketua Majelis Rendah Parlemen Rusia, Vyacheslav Volodin menyebut Johnson sebagai badut yang kini telah pergi. |â€œBadut itu telah pergi,â€ kata Vyacheslav Volodin|Sementara itu, Taipan Rusia, Oleg Deripaska, menilai mundurnya Johnson adalah akhir yang memalukan.|â€œYang hati nuraninya akan dirusak oleh puluhan ribu nyawa dalam konflik tidak masuk akal di Ukraina ini,â€ katanya. |Sedangkan, Juru Bicara Kremlin Dmitry Peskov mengatakan, Johnson tak menyukai Rusia, begitu pun Kremlin tak menyukainya.|"Dia tidak menyukai kami, dan kami juga tidak menyukainya," kata Peskov.|Sebagaimana informasi sebelumnya, Johnson telah acapkali mengkritik Putin.|Bahkan, sebelum Presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin mengerahkan pasukannya ke Ukraina pada 24 Februari lalu. |Johnson pernah menyebut Putin sebagai pemimpin Kremlin yang kejam.|(Tribun-Video.com/ Kompas.com)|Artikel ini telah tayang di Kompas.com dengan judul "Rusia Rayakan Kejatuhan Boris Johnson: Sang Badut Telah Pergi", Klik untuk baca: https://www.kompas.com/global/read/2022/07/07/201327570/rusia-rayakan-kejatuhan-boris-johnson-sang-badut-telah-pergi?page=all#page2.|Penulis : Danur Lambang Pristiandaru|Editor : Danur Lambang Pristiandaru|Host: Bima Maulana|VP: Reza Nova|#borisjohnson #borisjohnsonleft #pminggris

title: Penampakan MSAT alias Mas Bechi Tersangka Pencabulan Santriwati usai Berhasil Dijemput Paksa
description: JOMBANG, KOMPAS.TV - Kepolisian berhasil menjemput paksa Moch Subchi Azal Tsani (MSAT) alias Mas Bechi pada Kamis (7/7) malam di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah.||||Setelah aparat gabungan melakukan pengepungan di kompleks Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah selama kurang lebih 12 jam.||||Kapolda Jawa Timur Irjen Pol Nico Afinta mengatakan MSAT alias Mas Bechi akhirnya menyerahkan diri.||||Kata Nico, tersangka pencabulan terhadap santriwati itu selama ini bersembunyi di Ponpes Shiddiqiyyah.||||Baca Juga Cerita 15 Jam Pengepungan Pesantren Shiddiqiyyah, Mas Bechi pun Menyerah di Tengah Malam di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306966/cerita-15-jam-pengepungan-pesantren-shiddiqiyyah-mas-bechi-pun-menyerah-di-tengah-malam||||Mas Bechi tersangka pencabulan terhadap santriwati kemudian digelandang ke Mapolda Jawa Timur untuk kemudian dilakukan pemeriksaan lebih lanjut.||||Setelah dilakukan penangkapan, Kata Nico, pihaknya akan melakukan koordinasi dengan pihak Kejaksaan.||||"Saudara MSA dibawa ke Polda Jawa Timur, saat ini tim bersama dengan yang bersangkutan sedang dalam perjalanan. Perkembangan besok akan kami sampaikan," ujar Nico saat ditemui wartawan pada Kamis (7/7) malam.||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306986/penampakan-msat-alias-mas-bechi-tersangka-pencabulan-santriwati-usai-berhasil-dijemput-paksa

title: Humiliated Boris Johnson forced from power - BBC News
description: The British Prime Minister Boris Johnson has been forced to announce that he is stepping down, after days of political turmoil.|Mr Johnson made the statement in Downing Street after more than 50 ministers resigned from his government.   The final crisis for Mr Johnson began with the resignation of his Chancellor Rishi Sunak and Health Secretary Sajid Javid. |It followed a series of scandals and accusations that Mr Johnson lacked honesty and integrity and had repeatedly lied to his party and the country.  |Mr Johnson said he would remain in post until a new leader is chosen by his Conservative Party.  However some senior Conservatives have called on him to leave office immediately.|Huw Edwards present BBC News at Ten reporting by political editor Chris Mason.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: Star Trek: Strange New Worlds - Season 1 Review
description: Season 1 of Star Trek: Strange New Worlds is now streaming on Paramount+. Review by Scott Collura.||||Star Trek: Strange New Worlds' first season manages to recapture the joy of classic Trek in a way that perhaps many of us didn't know was missing until we experienced this show. Emotional, exciting, funny, and sometimes scary, this is a final frontier that is both old-school and brand-new, featuring great characters who all get their fair share of the action. In many ways, Star Trek has come full circle with Strange New Worlds after 55 years of storytelling. And it's all the better for it.|#IGN #StarTrek

title: Presiden Jokowi Tinjau Penataan Kawasan dan Rumah Layak Huni di Permukiman Belawan, 7 Juli 2022
description: *Presiden Jokowi Tinjau Penataan Kawasan dan Rumah Layak Huni di Permukiman Belawan*|Presiden Joko Widodo meninjau penataan kawasan dan rumah layak huni di Kecamatan Medan Belawan, Kota Medan, pada Kamis, 7 Juli 2022. Penataan kawasan dan rumah di permukiman Belawan merupakan bentuk kerja sama antara Badan Kependudukan dan Keluarga Berencana Nasional (BKKBN), Kementerian Pekerjaan Umum dan Perumahan Rakyat (PUPR), beserta pemerintah daerah. |â€œJadi yang ingin kita kerjakan di sini adalah penataan kawasan, penataan rumah-rumah yang layak huni dan sudah dimulai oleh pemerintah kota, kemudian nanti pemerintah pusat, PU, akan kebagian penataan kawasannya,â€ ujar Presiden. |Presiden berharap, adanya penataan kawasan dan rumah layak huni di permukiman Belawan dapat mengentaskan kemiskinan ekstrem di wilayah tersebut. |â€œJadi air bersihnya, sanitasi, jalan kampungnya, semuanya akan kita tata biar lebih sehat, baik,â€ lanjutnya. |Berdasarkan data dari BKKBN, sejumlah rumah di permukiman tersebut tercatat dalam kondisi tidak layak huni dengan tempat pembuangan air yang kurang baik. Untuk itu, diperlukan perbaikan rumah tersebut agar dapat mengurangi risiko _stunting_ atau kekerdilan pada keluarga. |Dalam perbaikan rumah tersebut, pemerintah menerapkan teknologi rumah sistem panel instan (Ruspin) yang merupakan salah satu pengembangan di bidang teknologi rancangan konstruksi bangunan rumah tinggal maupun bangunan umum lainnya. Dengan teknologi tersebut, desain bangunan dapat dibongkar pasang maupun dipasang secara permanen. |Turut mendampingi Presiden dalam peninjauan tersebut yakni Menteri Pekerjaan Umum dan Perumahan Rakyat (PUPR) Basuki Hadimuljono, Menteri Sekretaris Negara Pratikno, Kepala BKKBN Hasto Wardoyo, Gubernur Sumatra Utara Edy Rahmayadi, dan Wali Kota Medan Bobby Nasution. |Medan, 7 Juli 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: What are the odds?! Zalatoris' ball stops on Fitzpatrick's ball marker
description: During the first round of the 2022 Genesis Scottish Open, Will Zalatoris' chip shot saw the ball come to rest on top of the poker chip Matt Fitzpatrick uses as a ball marker. After determining the ruling, Zalatoris holed his par putt.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the best players on the PGA TOUR and the DP World Tour will compete against one another in the first co-sanctioned Genesis Scottish Open between the two tours. Players from each tour will be teeing it up at The Renaissance Club in North Berwick, including 2022 Travelers Champion Xander Schauffele, 2022 PGA Championship winner Justin Thomas, World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler and former World No. 1 John Rahm. U.S. Open Champion Matt Fitzpatrick will make his much-anticipated return at the Genesis Scottish Open and will be looking to build on his result last year, when he finished runner-up to Min Woo Lee, who defeated Fitzpatrick and Thomas Detry in a three-way playoff. Robert MacIntyre will be carrying the hopes of the home fans as the highest-ranked Scottish player in the field, while the top-ranked player on the DP World Tour, Will Zalatoris, who finished runner up at both the U.S. Open and the PGA Championship, will be hoping to turn his excellent form into his first win on either tour. ||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

title: Asteroid Bennuâ€™s Surprising Surface Revealed by NASA Spacecraft
description: Near-Earth asteroid Bennu is a rubble pile of rocks and boulders left over from the formation of the solar system. On October 20, 2020, NASAâ€™s OSIRIS-REx spacecraft briefly touched down on Bennu and collected a sample for return to Earth. During this â€œTAG event,â€ the spacecraftâ€™s arm sank far deeper into the asteroid than expected, confirming that Bennuâ€™s surface is incredibly weak. Now, scientists have used data from OSIRIS-REx to revisit the TAG event and better understand how Bennuâ€™s loose upper layers are held together.|Read more: https://www.nasa.gov/feature/goddard/2022/surprise-again-asteroid-bennu-reveals-its-surface-is-like-a-plastic-ball-pit/|Credit: NASAâ€™s Goddard Space Flight Center/CI Lab/SVS|Dan Gallagher (KBRwyle): Producer|Jonathan North (KBRwyle): Lead Animator|Kel Elkins (USRA): Lead Data Visualizer|Alexander Bodnar (AIMM): Animator|Adriana Manrique Gutierrez (KBRwyle): Animator|Walt Feimer (KBRwyle): Animator|Lisa Poje (Freelance): Animator|Dan Gallagher (KBRwyle): Narrator|Dante Lauretta (The University of Arizona): Lead Scientist|Kevin Walsh (SwRI): Scientist|Ronald Ballouz (JHUAPL): Scientist|Olivier Barnouin (JHUAPL): Scientist|Rani Gran (NASA/GSFC): Public Affairs Officer|Nancy Neal-Jones (NASA/GSFC): Public Affairs Officer|James Tralie (ADNET): Support|Ernie Wright (USRA): Support|Aaron E.
